# Facet plot


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
p=ggplot(tips, aes(tip,total_bill,)) + geom_point(aes(color=sex)) + facet_wrap("day")
p
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](1-ggplot2_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-19-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::

make 3 plot per row


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
p=ggplot(tips, aes(tip,total_bill,)) + geom_point(aes(color=sex)) + facet_wrap("day",ncol = 3)
p
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](1-ggplot2_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-20-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::




# title,size,x y name




## add title


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
p=ggplot(tips, aes(tip, total_bill,color=sex)) + geom_point()+ ggtitle("tip by sex")
p
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](1-ggplot2_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-21-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::






## adjust size




::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
p=ggplot(tips, aes(tip, total_bill,color=sex)) + geom_point()+ ggtitle("tip by sex")+theme(
  plot.margin = margin(2, 2, 5, 5, "cm"))
p
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](1-ggplot2_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-22-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::




## change x y name



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
p=ggplot(tips, aes(tip, total_bill,color=sex)) + geom_point()+ scale_x_continuous(name="new x name")+ scale_y_continuous(name="new y name")
p
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](1-ggplot2_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-23-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::


# applying themes

