## theme_bw()

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
p=ggplot(tips, aes(tip, total_bill,color=sex)) + geom_point()+ scale_x_continuous(name="new x name")+ scale_y_continuous(name="new y name")
p+ theme_bw()
```

